ZH: 今天天气真好。
EN: The weather is really nice today.

ZH: 昨天晚上很冷。
EN: It was very cold last night.

ZH: 天上有一颗明亮的星星。
EN: There is a bright star in the sky.

ZH: 他今天有点不舒服。
EN: He is feeling a bit unwell today.

ZH: 星期天是我的休息日。
EN: Sunday is my day off.

ZH: 天黑了，时间过得真快。
EN: It's getting dark, time flies.

ZH: 在这个美丽的地方，天真的很美。
EN: In this beautiful place, the sky is really beautiful.

ZH: 她总是乐观地看待每一天。
EN: She always looks at every day optimistically.

ZH: 是多云的天气，我们可能会有雨。
EN: It's cloudy weather, we might have rain.

ZH: 他对自己的前途充满信心，仿佛天塌下来也能够支持下来。
EN: He is confident in his future, as if he can support himself even if the sky falls.

ZH: 在天黑之前记得点上蜡烛。
EN: Remember to light a candle before it gets dark.

ZH: 这个星期天我们可以去郊外玩。
EN: We can go out to the countryside this Sunday.

ZH: 他是我生命中的宝贝，我真的很爱他。
EN: He is the treasure of my life, I really love him.

ZH: 爷爷告诉我，每天看看蓝天对心情好。
EN: Grandpa told me that looking at the blue sky every day is good for the mood.

ZH: 每天早晨，太阳升起，带给我们新的希望。
EN: Every morning, the sun rises, bringing us new hope.

ZH: 我猜今天的天气可能会下雪。
EN: I think it might snow today.

ZH: 星期天晚上，我们会一起去看电影。
EN: We will go see a movie together on Sunday night.

ZH: 天气越来越冷，应该多穿衣服。
EN: The weather is getting colder, we should wear more clothes.

ZH: 昨天他跟我说的每一句话我都记得。
EN: I remember every word he said to me yesterday.

ZH: 不管天气怎么样，我们都会在一起。
EN: No matter what the weather is like, we will be together.
